 class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore various types of areas. Each area has a unique atmosphere and story. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Solve puzzles and find hints to reveal secrets and mysteries that are undisclosed for a long time. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1985960/extras/45191b44e169263c00ba866c1d109196.avif?t=1766032537\" width=616 height=130 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1985960/extras/aeeff0e76ece41ee6bbda0e0fc1b13d9.poster.avif?t=1766032537\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1985960/extras/aeeff0e76ece41ee6bbda0e0fc1b13d9.webm?t=1766032537\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1985960/extras/aeeff0e76ece41ee6bbda0e0fc1b13d9.mp4?t=1766032537\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >From recognizable classic puzzles to unique ones, various types of puzzles are waiting for you to visit. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1985960/extras/ff0149d5837baa0c5e78753b22db1622.avif?t=1766032537\" width=616 height=130 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1985960/extras/e0e8799777f68684da200b238dacbe98.poster.avif?t=1766032537\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1985960/extras/e0e8799777f68684da200b238dacbe98.webm?t=1766032537\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1985960/extras/e0e8799777f68684da200b238dacbe98.mp4?t=1766032537\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The power of the Great One has been shattered and lots of vicious adversaries are keen on gathering the scattered pieces of the Great One’s power. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Overcome these fearsome enemies to save the world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1985960/extras/18df9ad2df69066e9bd5b7ab0cd9c7e2.avif?t=1766032537\" width=616 height=130 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1985960/extras/0a8bd4094eff011b1bbe2bb5f94537ea.poster.avif?t=1766032537\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1985960/extras/0a8bd4094eff011b1bbe2bb5f94537ea.webm?t=1766032537\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1985960/extras/0a8bd4094eff011b1bbe2bb5f94537ea.mp4?t=1766032537\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Hats and Masks</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Put on your explorer’s hat and go find various awesome hats and masks! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dress Baby Ogu with these items and some of them might have some special skills attached. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Drawings</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are many landmarks out there.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Draw fancy objects and landscapes to discover new lands and you might also find hints in them.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Friends</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Meet friends on your journey and help those in need.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >They might help you with their unique skills or gifts. You’re not alone in this world!</p>",
